{"tid":764781,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡少芬歎紅酒享天倫","createTime":"2018-08-02T08:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T08:40:49.000Z","uid":48905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"baee30b076380e181d7521dbd63ad6bdf19189e1","tid":764781,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T08:44:08.000Z","msg":"藝人蔡少芬十分重視親子活動，與丈夫張晉帶同兩個囡囡張楚兒（湯圓）及張信兒（包子）到主題樂園遊玩。兩名女兒長高了不少，在酒店房興奮影不停，蔡少芬則相當識歎，品嘗紅酒，一家四口玩得盡興。她在社交網發文：「如果每天這樣過，真的是圖畫故事的主角。我是不是做夢啊？（學包子說的話！）」。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/164043_0490b9e9deb0a7546bec6c5a6202b9a7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F164043_0490b9e9deb0a7546bec6c5a6202b9a7.png&h=29eab087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> 可愛的女兒&hellip;</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/164321_f30ca2f085a29be70ad3778cf86da13f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F164321_f30ca2f085a29be70ad3778cf86da13f.png&h=d0bf63b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> 蔡少芬飲紅酒，看似寫意。</span>"},{"pid":"e6fab980319fb91374a6a4f9af6651522c03d5df","tid":764781,"uid":51183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T08:59:34.000Z","msg":"你對邊個好？你對Ada唔好咩？"},{"pid":"ab184aec0847687b596bbc1010cf618b5143964a","tid":764781,"uid":59920,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/170132_aa2e2d933140aafafb454e6d93d2d40e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F170132_aa2e2d933140aafafb454e6d93d2d40e.jpg&h=c8b4f5c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/170229_38a7c07d6e1086bcae1359cc538d5c22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.li